# TEAM PROFILE

Team: Tottenham Hotspur
League: EPL
Season: 2025–26

---

## Squad Overview

### Core Players (First XI level)

| Player | Role | Key Strengths | Key Weaknesses | Tactical Notes |
|------|------|--------------|---------------|----------------|
| Guglielmo Vicario | GK | Reflexes, sweeping | Aerial control | Enables high line |
| Cristian Romero | RCB | Aggression, duels | Discipline | Steps out aggressively |
| Micky van de Ven | LCB | Recovery pace | Aerial duels | Protects high line |
| Destiny Udogie | LB | Ball carrying | Positioning | Key build-up outlet |
| Yves Bissouma | DM | Press resistance | Consistency | Central pivot |
| Pape Sarr | CM | Physicality | Final ball | Box-to-box engine |
| James Maddison | AM | Creativity | Defensive work | Primary creator |
| Son Heung-min | LW | Runs in behind | Aerials | Transition threat |
| Richarlison | ST | Physical duels | Link play | Target option |

### Rotation Players

| Player | Role | Key Strengths | Key Weaknesses | Tactical Notes |
|------|------|--------------|---------------|----------------|
| Brennan Johnson | RW | Pace | Decision making | Vertical threat |
| Pierre-Emile Højbjerg | CM | Positioning | Mobility | Game control |
| Dejan Kulusevski | RW | Ball retention | Pace | In-possession option |

